						<summary>

						<p>On a stone standing at the entrance into a Muhammaden's house.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1562, Svabhānu, Chaitra, ba. 15.</p>						

						<p>Records the renovation of the <hi rend="italic">Śikhara</hi> of the temple of Chennakēśava at Nallaballe by Tippā-Reḍḍi, during the regime <hi rend="italic">(doratana)</hi> of Pemmasāni Chinna Timmā-Nāyaka and the administration of Kaṁbhaṁ Pāpi-Reḍḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
